<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="about-page">

  <!-- Hero banner -->
  <div class="about-hero">
    <span class="about-eyebrow">Welcome to হাতেখড়ি</span>
    <h1>Hathekhori</h1>
    <p class="about-tagline">Every journey begins with a first stroke.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Who We Are -->
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="about-section-inner">
      <div class="about-text">
        <span class="about-label">Who We Are</span>
        <h2>A Home for India's Living Crafts</h2>
        <p>Hathekhori is a handmade crafts brand rooted in the rich artistic traditions of India. We are a collective of craft lovers, designers, and storytellers who believe that every handmade object carries a piece of its maker's soul — their patience, their skill, and their culture.</p>
        <p>The name <strong>হাতেখড়ি</strong> comes from a Bengali ceremony where a child writes their first letters — the very first moment of creation. That spirit of beginning, of making something from nothing, is at the heart of everything we do.</p>
        <p>We work directly with artisans from West Bengal, Rajasthan, Bihar, Maharashtra, and beyond — preserving ancient crafts like Madhubani painting, Warli art, hand block printing, and tribal jewellery by bringing them into the lives of modern homes.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-image-block">
        <img src="/images/madhubani.jpg" alt="Madhubani Art" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Want to Achieve -->
  <section class="about-section about-section-alt">
    <div class="about-section-inner about-section-inner-reverse">
      <div class="about-image-block">
        <img src="/images/warli.jpeg" alt="Warli Art" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <span class="about-label">Our Mission</span>
        <h2>What We Want to Achieve</h2>
        <p>India has thousands of craft traditions that are slowly disappearing — not because they are less beautiful, but because they lack visibility and market access. We want to change that.</p>
        <p>Our goal is to build a bridge between the artisan's workshop and the modern consumer — making it easy to discover, appreciate, and own genuinely handmade objects that carry history, story, and craft.</p>
        <ul class="about-goals">
          <li>
            <span class="about-goal-icon">🤝</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Empower Artisans</strong>
              <p>Fair pay, direct partnerships, and a platform that puts the maker's story front and centre.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="about-goal-icon">🌿</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Sustain Crafts</strong>
              <p>Keep traditional art forms alive by creating genuine demand for authentic, handmade work.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="about-goal-icon">🏡</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Bring Craft Home</strong>
              <p>Make it simple for every household to own something meaningful — a piece of Indian craft heritage.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values strip -->
  <section class="about-values">
    <div class="about-value">
      <span class="about-value-num">500+</span>
      <span class="about-value-label">Years of Craft Tradition</span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-value">
      <span class="about-value-num">Handmade</span>
      <span class="about-value-label">Every Single Piece</span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-value">
      <span class="about-value-num">Artisan</span>
      <span class="about-value-label">Direct Partnerships</span>
    </div>
    <div class="about-value">
      <span class="about-value-num">India</span>
      <span class="about-value-label">Made with Pride</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="about-cta">
    <h2>Discover Our Craft Collection</h2>
    <p>Each piece is handpicked, handmade, and full of story. Browse our shop and find something that speaks to you.</p>
    <a href="/#shop" class="about-cta-btn">Explore the Collection</a>
  </section>

</div>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
